name: ANNIE Named Entity Recognizer
shortDescription: The ANNIE named entity recognition service. Identifies names of persons, locations, organizations, as well as money amounts, time and date expressions.

name: AnnoMarket News Pipeline
shortDescription: The AnnoMarket News Pipeline is a named entity recognition pipeline dedicated to the news domain. It combines text mining tools from the University of Sheffield with the Press Association's extensive knowledge base of newsworthy entities.

name: TwitIE Named Entity Recognizer for Tweets
shortDescription: Named entity recognition service for Twitter data. Identifies person, location, organization etc. and also performs normalization of abbreviations and common shorthands ("brb", "gr8", "2day",etc.).

name: AnnoMarket Political Speech Categoriser
shortDescription: The AnnoMarket Political Speech Categoriser is a text classification pipeline dedicated to analysing political speech. It will attempt to associate each input sentence with one of the categories it was trained to recognise.

name: Generic Opinion Mining (English)
shortDescription: Recognises "opinionated" sentences in English text or Tweets and classifies them as positive or negative, with a score indicating the strength of the sentiment. This pipeline was developed by the Arcomem project.

name: DBpedia LOD Gazetteer
shortDescription: DBpedia linked open data gazetteer. It identifies people, organizations and geographical locations in the input text and assigns them the corresponding DBpedia URI.

name: DBpedia Locations Gazetteer
shortDescription: DBpedia linked open data gazetteer pipeline. It identifies geographical location names in the input text and assigns them the corresponding DBpedia URIs.

name: DBpedia Organizations Gazetteer
shortDescription: DBpedia linked open data gazetteer pipeline. It identifies organization names in the input text and assigns them corresponding DBpedia URIs.

name: DBpedia Person Names Gazetteer
shortDescription: DBpedia linked open data gazetteer pipeline. It identifies person names in the input text and assigns them corresponding DBpedia URIs.

name: Freebase LOD Gazetteer
shortDescription: Freebase linked open data gazetteer. It identifies people, organizations and geographical locations in the input text and assigns them the corresponding Freebase URI.

name: Freebase Locations Gazetteer
shortDescription: Freebase linked open data gazetteer pipeline. It identifies geographical location names in the input text and assigns them the corresponding Freebase URI.

name: Freebase Organizations Gazetteer
shortDescription: Freebase linked open data gazetteer pipeline. It identifies organization names in the input text and assigns them the corresponding Freebase URI.

name: Freebase Person Names Gazetteer
shortDescription: Freebase linked open data gazetteer pipeline. It identifies person names in the input text and assigns them the corresponding Freebase URI.

name: GeoNames Open Linked Data Gazetteer Pipeline
shortDescription: GeoNames linked data gazetteer pipeline, recognizing more than eight million geographical locations.

name: Arabic Named Entity Recognizer
shortDescription: A named entity recognition service for documents in the Arabic language.Based on ANNIE, it identifies names of persons, locations,organizations, as well as money amounts, time and dateexpressions.

name: French Named Entity Recognizer
shortDescription: A named entity recognition service for documents in the French language.Based on ANNIE, it identifies names of persons, locations,organizations, as well as money amounts, time and dateexpressions.

name: German Named Entity Recognizer
shortDescription: A named entity recognition service for documents in the German language.Based on ANNIE, it identifies names of persons, locations,organizations, as well as money amounts, time and dateexpressions.

name: Romanian Named Entity Recognizer
shortDescription: A named entity recognition service for documents in the Romanian language.Based on ANNIE, it identifies names of persons, locations,organizations, as well as money amounts, time and dateexpressions.

name: Russian Named Entity Recognizer (basic)
shortDescription: A named entity recognition service for documents in the Russian language.Based on ANNIE, it identifies names of persons, locations,organizations, as well as money amounts, time and dateexpressions.

name: Russian NER (with inflexional gazetteer and orthomatcher)
shortDescription: A named entity recognition service for documents in the Russian language.Based on ANNIE, it identifies names of persons, locations,organizations, as well as money amounts, time and dateexpressions.

name: CLaRK NLP Pipeline (Bulgarian)
shortDescription: CLaRK System based processing pipeline for Bulgarian. The pipeline consists of tokenization, part-of-speech tagging, morphology analysis & disambiguation, named entities recognition.

name: Measurement expression annotator
shortDescription: Annotates numbers and measurement expressions, with their normalised values in SI units.

name: ANNIE+Measurements
shortDescription: Annotates named entities (person, location, organization, date) as well as numbers and measurement expressions.

name: PennBio Tagger
shortDescription: Tokeniser tuned to biomedical text, and taggers for gene, genomic variations and malignancy type entities, from the University of Pennsylvania.

name: AbGene Tagger
shortDescription: Tag mentions of gene entities in text using the AbGene tagger.

name: OpenNLP English Pipeline
shortDescription: The English tokeniser, sentence splitter, POS tagger, phrase chunker and named-entity recogniser from Apache OpenNLP.

name: OpenNLP Dutch Pipeline
shortDescription: The Dutch tokeniser, sentence splitter, POS tagger, phrase chunker and named-entity recogniser from Apache OpenNLP.

name: OpenNLP German Pipeline
shortDescription: The German tokeniser, sentence splitter and POS tagger from Apache OpenNLP.

name: Hunpos English POS Tagger
shortDescription: Tokeniser, sentence splitter, and part-of-speech tagging for English using the Hunpos HMM-based tagger.

name: Hunpos Hungarian POS Tagger
shortDescription: Tokeniser, sentence splitter, and part-of-speech tagging for Hungarian using the Hunpos HMM-based tagger.

name: Stanford Parser and POS Tagger
shortDescription: The Stanford Parser, producing POS tags, parse trees and dependency structures for input text.

name: Stanford Parser with Heptag POS Tagging
shortDescription: The Stanford Parser, producing parse trees and dependency structures for input text. This version also adds POS tags using the standard ANNIE POS tagger.

name: Noun Phrase Chunker
shortDescription: Base Noun Phrase Chunker, producing NounChunk annotations.

name: HepTag POS Tagger
shortDescription: Annotates Token and Sentence in English text, adding a POS tag to each token as the "category" feature.

name: POS Tagging and Morphological Analysis
shortDescription: Annotates Token and Sentence in English text, adding a POS tag and morphological root and affix to each token.

name: Snowball Stemmer (English)
shortDescription: Tokeniser and Snowball Stemmer for English.

name: Snowball Stemmer (French)
shortDescription: Tokeniser and Snowball Stemmer for French.
